ReVamp - Wild Card (Digipak Edition)  mp3  320k  a2k 2013 What we got...Wild Card is the second album by the Dutch progressive metal band ReVamp. The album was released on 23 August 2013 in Europe, on 26 August in the UK and on 3 September 2013 in the USA.
